<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Resource_management_arm  Entity: Resource_event  
   <express_ref linkend="resource_management:arm:Resource_management_arm.Resource_event"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Resource_management_arm.Resource_event">
A <b>Resource_event</b> is an event that affects the balance or availability of a managed resource. The role
of a resource event is determined by classification.
<note number="1">
A resource event can be classified as "Planned" or "Actual".
</note>
</ext_description>
