<ext_description linkend="Resource_management_arm.Resource_event_correspondence_relationship">
A <b>Resource_event_correspondence_relationship</b> is a relationship between a resource event and a corresponding statement of 
<express_ref linkend="required_resource:arm:Required_resource_arm.Required_resource"/>. 
<note number="1">A resource event correspondence relationship can be classified as "Designated for".
</note>
<note number="2">A resource event can be planned or recorded without having a corresponding resource requirement statement.
</note>
</ext_description>
