  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Resource_management_arm.Resource_location">
A <b>Resource_location</b> is a location where a managed resource can be found. The role
of a location is determined by classification.

<note number = "1">The location can be a warehouse, a shelf in warehouse, an organizational unit, or
a serilized product that can be cannibalized .
</note>
